Syntax: bload <bow> <arrow>

Bload is the command to load an arrow into a bow.  Once a bow is loaded,
you will automatically hold the bow.  Hence, you may not use the bload
command unless both hands are free.

Bload will also check any held/worn quivers for the arrow.

See Also : SHOOT, REMOVE, RESTRING, RANGED WEAPONS
Related Topics: COMBAT
